# Walkthrough — GoLive UI Redesign 🎮

## Root Cause Fixed

The entire site was broken because [globals.css](file:///C:/GoLive/app/globals.css) was missing two critical Tailwind v4 directives:

```diff
+@import "tailwindcss";
+
+@theme {
+  --color-background: #0e0e10;
+  --color-surface: #18181b;
+  --color-primary: #9147ff;
+  /* ... 15+ tokens */
+}
```

Without these, **none** of the Tailwind utility classes (`flex`, `bg-primary`, `rounded-xl`, etc.) were being generated.

## What Changed

| File | Changes |
|------|---------|
| [globals.css](file:///C:/GoLive/app/globals.css) | Added `@import`, `@theme`, redesigned color palette (Twitch-dark), custom components |
| [Navbar.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/components/Navbar.tsx) | YouTube-style centered search with button, circular action buttons |
| [Sidebar.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/components/Sidebar.tsx) | Twitch-style live channels with viewer counts, active nav indicator |
| [Layout.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/components/Layout.tsx) | Proper sidebar offset with responsive mobile override |
| [VideoCard.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/components/VideoCard.tsx) | LIVE badge support, 16:9 aspect-ratio, hover overlay |
| [page.tsx](file:///C:/GoLive/app/page.tsx) | Interactive category chips, 12 videos incl. live stream |
| [watch page](file:///C:/GoLive/app/watch/[id]/page.tsx) | YouTube action buttons, Twitch chat with 9 messages |
| [login](file:///C:/GoLive/app/login/page.tsx) / [register](file:///C:/GoLive/app/register/page.tsx) | Cleaned up with new tokens |
| [upload](file:///C:/GoLive/app/upload/page.tsx) | Simplified drop zone, cleaner form |
| [profile](file:///C:/GoLive/app/profile/[username]/page.tsx) | YouTube-style tabs, 4 video cards, circular avatar |

## Design Palette

- **Background**: `#0e0e10` (Twitch dark)
- **Surface**: `#18181b` (cards, inputs)
- **Primary**: `#9147ff` (Twitch purple)
- **Accent**: `#00e6cb` (teal highlights)
- **Border**: `#2f2f35` (subtle dividers)

## How to Verify

Your dev server at `http://localhost:3001` should auto-reload. Check:
1. **Home** — Video grid with category chips
2. **Watch** (`/watch/1`) — Player + chat sidebar
3. **Profile** (`/profile/FragMaster`) — Banner + tabs + videos
4. **Login** / **Register** — Auth forms
5. **Upload** — Drag-and-drop interface
